      "title": "Covid-19 on the rise with 2 deaths reported yesterday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two people who were being treated for the covid-19 virus died yesterday and 75 people infected with the virus were reported, the Director General of Government Information announced",
        "With that, the total number of corona patients reported from this country has increased to 664,975.",
        "It further stated the deceased two persons have been identified as a woman and a man above the age of 60"
